channel.title: Are You Still There? - Mr. Serpent [Ambient/Chill]
channel.description:
Hellooo! Chip from [freeform](https://soundcloud.com/freeformrecs) here, with our latest release featuring @MrSerpent! "Are You Still There" is an emotional ambient track that I personally enjoy very much, and I'm sure you probably will too.
Stream on SC: https://soundcloud.com/freeformrecs/ff003 DL on Bandcamp: https://freeformrecs.bandcamp.com/track/are-you-still-there Spotify: coming soon!
![FFserp|300x300](upload://fTaq3x7Gp7d87yzOt6Q4C9hMIhj.jpg)
P.S. Go follow Mr. Serpent! His SoundCloud is https://soundcloud.com/misterserpent
